 This, uh =E2=80=A6=C2=A0this just about barely fulfills that requirement? =
Maybe? I=E2=80=99m sure the SEC will have comments. But it=E2=80=99s a star=
t.Anyway a few miscellaneous tidbits from the filing:=09It is a rule of SPA=
Cs that, when a SPAC goes public, it can=E2=80=99t already have a deal line=
d up. =E2=80=9CWe have not selected any specific business combination targe=
t and we have not, nor has anyone on our behalf, initiated any substantive =
