I love the idea that a bunch of disgruntled junior analysts at Goldman Sach=
s Group Inc. went to their bosses with a carefully reasoned presentation sa=
ying, like, =E2=80=9Cwe work 100 hours a week and we=E2=80=99re dying,=E2=
=80=9D and Goldman=E2=80=99s senior exectuives=C2=A0said =E2=80=9Cthank you=
