=9D [Goldman=E2=80=99s memo]=C2=A0said.I love it.=C2=A0I assume that if you=
=E2=80=99ve made partner at Goldman you are not going to just laze around t=
he beach all summer; nobody in a position to make use of this is going to a=
buse it.I=C2=A0will say! If you run a lucrative financial partnership and y=
ou find yourself =E2=80=9Cfocusing=C2=A0on the experience=E2=80=9D of your =
junior employees, that=E2=80=99s a decent position to be in. The implicatio=
n there is that there=E2=80=99s too much work, the junior people are workin=
g too hard, and so the partners are making too much money. Great! If you ru=
n a lucrative financial partnership and you find yourself =E2=80=9Cfocusing=
