. Having a good partnership experience is the point of the partnership! Obv=
iously Goldman Sachs is not an actual partnership anymore; it is a publicly=
 traded corporation with =E2=80=9Cpartner=E2=80=9D as something of a courte=
sy title. Apparently the partner experience needs some work.
