oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">here it is</a> =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0and of course I will discuss it, because it is funny and bec=
ause that is what I do for a living. But in a sense there is no=C2=A0<em>po=
int=C2=A0</em>in reading it. It will not tell you much about TMTG=E2=80=99s=
 business, because TMTG doesn=E2=80=99t have much of a business. Sure it ha=
s no real revenue,[1] but it also has almost no=C2=A0<em>expenses</em>. In =
2021 (the only period for which it has=C2=A0financial statements), TMTG had=
