proximately 40 full-time employees.=E2=80=9D Twitter Inc., a real social me=
dia company that TMTG supposedly competes with, spent <a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/27733329.285614/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmd=
