ay</a>=C2=A0</em>on operating expenses last quarter.</p><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">Here is TMTG=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/27733329.285614/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdh=
