y, the enterprise value of the most direct competitor to TMTG=E2=80=99s fir=
st product, TruthSocial, was $41 billion. Therefore, Digital World=E2=80=99=
s management believed that $875 million with a potential earnout of an addi=
tional $825 million was a reasonable estimate of TMTG=E2=80=99s enterprise =
valuation and applied it to the Business Combination.</p></blockquote><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That is: =E2=80=9CTwitter is worth $41 billion, so =
surely Truth Social is worth at least $1.7 billion.=E2=80=9D I mean: Fine! =
